{"tid":2204405,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"年近六旬主婦認5月24日堵路 蘇惠德今決定判監4天緩刑12個月","createTime":"2020-09-16T04:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T08:12:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a2e108489a3111962dd0a54c0601fd0e839d5660","tid":2204405,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"昨日報導:<br />\n年近六旬主婦認5月24日堵路 稱不滿國安法無諮詢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2203156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2203156</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9452&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=6bde5d38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9452</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#蘇惠德總裁判官 <br />\n#20200524銅鑼灣 #判刑<br />\n<br />\n張（59）<br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n被告於2020年9月15日同意案情，被告認罪<br />\n總裁判官裁定罪名成立❗️總裁判官在詢問主控案情詳情後，未能完全確定所有細節，故索取cctv再作判刑<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n5月24日有網民號召遊行，有遊行人士向灣仔方向出發，有人堵路，燒雜物，打爛櫥窗等，當日晚上警員接報到附近巡邏，見到被告並監視約一分鐘，目睹被告於軒尼斯道481號電車路放置雜物。<br />\n<br />\n經總裁判官問控方，得知被告所在的行車段的較前位置已被堵路，故該段行車路並無車輛通過。<br />\n<br />\n自辯求情<br />\n1. 被捕後坐左48小時<br />\n2. 賣冰狗二代多證據卻獲撤控<br />\n3. 國安法很急推出，市民無法表達意見<br />\n4. 衝動犯事<br />\n<br />\n判刑：6天監禁，認罪扣1/3，共4天監禁，緩刑12個月<br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n相關片段回顧 (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CAk-PBsAJDj/?igshid=3vu6j7177gp2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAk-PBsAJDj%2F%3Figshid%3D3vu6j7177gp2&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=f1c8fd4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAk-PBsAJDj%2F%3Figshid%3D3vu6j7177gp2&h=d97f7c12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CAk-PBsAJDj/?igshid=3vu6j7177gp2</a>)（非法庭播放片段，僅為被捕片段）"},{"pid":"9307cbfe468bbdbac42501aa42f18a6c962fd47c","tid":2204405,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"a984e30dccf0ce44b4f04ea1a2a7de666cc2b4fc","tid":2204405,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T04:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de4dc29aa02db03bb24708bff38ceb3fa5cc4ad","tid":2204405,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a984e30dccf0ce44b4f04ea1a2a7de666cc2b4fc","tid":2204405,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T04:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7687795569c52da2ff561c2678f4fd4208a26e","tid":2204405,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9307cbfe468bbdbac42501aa42f18a6c962fd47c","tid":2204405,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"cls"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7a4c1824b731c9b3ddb4de4f43a1b758709e16","tid":2204405,"uid":274532,"like"